Products.RichDescription:
A tea fit for an Earl!

Legend has it that Earl Grey was developed especially for the 1800s. It is light and aromatic with a distinctive citrus bergamot flavour. So sip and enjoy this delightful blend inspired by the Earl and you will feel like you have just stepped back in time.

In 1706, Thomas Twining started selling tea. More than 500 years on, the Twining tradition continues with our finest blends for you to Enjoy Every Day.

Products.Name: Masterfoods Chilli Flakes
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Masterfoods Chilli Flakes' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Chilli Flakes are commonly used to add heat or spice to your meal. Used in Mexican dishes and curries.
Easily add depth and flavour to your cooking with MasterFoods™ Chilli Flakes. A savoury herb with a floral aroma and slightly warming peppermint aftertaste. Dried flakes of fresh red chilli used commonly to add heat or a 'bite' to your favourite meals. Widely used in Mexican and Asian cooking to deliver meals of varying spice levels. Sprinkle into an Asian stir-fry and rice dinner or stir through your Mexican mince.
MasterFoods™ Established in 1945
Grown with Integrity, sourced with Pride.

Products.RichDescription:
This delicious pasta sauce is rich in flavour, made from real tomatoes, and just the perfect amount to heat and serve over steaming pasta for a quick and tasty meal for two.

Ready in 60 seconds
Medium Heat Rating
Meal in a hurry! This delicious pasta sauce is rich in flavour, made from real tomatoes, and just the perfect amount to heat and serve over steaming pasta for a quick and tasty meal for 2.
No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.
Cooking Instructions:
In a microwave...
1. Cut open the pouch corner
2. Heat for 60 seconds at 1000 W*
3. Serve over steaming pasta and you’ve got a delicious pasta meal in minutes!
*For different powered microwaves, adjust heating time to manufacturer's instructions.
Why not try adding a cup of steamed vegetables.

Dolmio® believes in the value of sharing a meal together.

This pasta sauce helps you create a delicious and wholesome meal that can be enjoyed any day of the week.

Medium Heat Rating
